<ns1706:section xmlns:ns1706="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.concepts.architecture.examples.cofLoader.generating.selectingPerformanceTactics">

  <ns1707:title xmlns:ns1707="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Selecting performance tactics</ns1707:title>
  <ns1708:para xmlns:ns1708="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    The core strategies for realizing performance are
    <ns1709:itemizedlist xmlns:ns1709="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      <ns1710:listitem xmlns:ns1710="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1711:para xmlns:ns1711="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">managing resource demand,</ns1711:para></ns1710:listitem>
      <ns1712:listitem xmlns:ns1712="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1713:para xmlns:ns1713="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">managing the resources themselves, and</ns1713:para></ns1712:listitem>
      <ns1714:listitem xmlns:ns1714="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1715:para xmlns:ns1715="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">managing resource sharing.</ns1715:para></ns1714:listitem>
    </ns1709:itemizedlist>
  </ns1708:para>
  
  <ns1716:section xmlns:ns1716="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    <ns1717:title xmlns:ns1717="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">What resources required by the application?</ns1717:title>
    <ns1718:para xmlns:ns1718="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      The application requires
      <ns1719:itemizedlist xmlns:ns1719="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        <ns1720:listitem xmlns:ns1720="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1721:para xmlns:ns1721="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">processing resources,</ns1721:para></ns1720:listitem>
        <ns1722:listitem xmlns:ns1722="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1723:para xmlns:ns1723="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">the client  and policy databases,</ns1723:para></ns1722:listitem>
        <ns1724:listitem xmlns:ns1724="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1725:para xmlns:ns1725="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">bandwidth between the application node and the database node.</ns1725:para></ns1724:listitem>
      </ns1719:itemizedlist>
    </ns1718:para>
  </ns1716:section>
  
  <ns1726:section xmlns:ns1726="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    <ns1727:title xmlns:ns1727="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Tactics available for resource demand management</ns1727:title>
    <ns1728:para xmlns:ns1728="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      Tactics available for managing resource demand include
      <ns1729:itemizedlist xmlns:ns1729="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        <ns1730:listitem xmlns:ns1730="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1731:para xmlns:ns1731="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">improve the efficiency of resource usage,</ns1731:para></ns1730:listitem>
        <ns1732:listitem xmlns:ns1732="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1733:para xmlns:ns1733="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">manage the event rate, and</ns1733:para></ns1732:listitem>
        <ns1734:listitem xmlns:ns1734="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1735:para xmlns:ns1735="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">control the sampling frequency.</ns1735:para></ns1734:listitem>
      </ns1729:itemizedlist>
      Of these the last is not relevant and we shall try and employ the first two.
    </ns1728:para>
  </ns1726:section>
  
  <ns1736:section xmlns:ns1736="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    <ns1737:title xmlns:ns1737="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Tactics available for resource management</ns1737:title>
    <ns1738:para xmlns:ns1738="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      The tactics available for resource management include
      <ns1739:itemizedlist xmlns:ns1739="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
        <ns1740:listitem xmlns:ns1740="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1741:para xmlns:ns1741="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">increasing the available resources,</ns1741:para></ns1740:listitem>
        <ns1742:listitem xmlns:ns1742="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1743:para xmlns:ns1743="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">supporting concurrencies, and</ns1743:para></ns1742:listitem>
        <ns1744:listitem xmlns:ns1744="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><ns1745:para xmlns:ns1745="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">replication.</ns1745:para></ns1744:listitem>
      </ns1739:itemizedlist>
      The first is, according to the client, not an option. We shall try and employ the latter two.
    </ns1738:para>
  </ns1736:section>
  
  <ns1746:section xmlns:ns1746="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    <ns1747:title xmlns:ns1747="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Tactics available for managing resource sharing</ns1747:title>
    <ns1748:para xmlns:ns1748="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
      We shall use both, <ns1749:emphasis xmlns:ns1749="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">scheduling</ns1749:emphasis> and <ns1750:emphasis xmlns:ns1750="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">queuing</ns1750:emphasis>.
    </ns1748:para>
  </ns1746:section>
</ns1706:section>